from typing import List
import numpy as np

def entrance(A: List[List[float]], k: int) -> List[List[float]]:
    A = np.array(A)
    (U, S, Vt) = np.linalg.svd(A, full_matrices=False)
    reconstructed_A = np.dot(U[:, :k] / S[:k], Vt[:k, :])
    return reconstructed_A.tolist()
